      "board_id": "3affd006-fd2b-4e7a-98af-82f94ac04d11",
      "title": "tmux：快捷键",
      "content": "ctrlb+c 创建新的窗口\r\nctrlb+% 将当前panel分割为左右两个panel\r\nexit 杀死某个panel、窗口或会话\r\nctrlb+d 将当前会话与窗口分离（不杀死，回到zsh）\r\nctrlb <n> 切换到第n个窗口\r\nctrlb w 列出所有窗口切换\r\nctrlb ， 重命名窗口",
      "description": "",
      "tags": [
        "tmux"
      ],
      "is_favorite": false,
      "created_at": "2026-03-25T15:04:09.249362",
      "updated_at": "2026-03-25T15:04:09.249362"
    },
    {
