      "description": "除gy245外，其他服务器需要将这个命令加到~/.zshrc才能联网",
      "tags": [
        "gy"
      ],
      "is_favorite": false,
      "created_at": "2026-03-19T17:25:40.582838",
      "updated_at": "2026-03-25T15:18:46.522307"
